    "description": "<p><span>You imbue a Melee Weapon you are wielding with crackling energy.</span></p><p><span>The next <strong>Attack Check </strong>that hits make with this weapon sheaths the target in booming energy.</span></p><p><span>If the target leaves or is moved from the current Space they are in, they automatically take 2 </span>Lightning <span>damage and the Spell ends. </span></p><p><span>This effect can be “stacked” multiple times from the same or different sources.</span></p><p></p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> This spell will toggle off when you use it with your weapon, but if you want you can reset it manually.</em></p><p></p><p><span><strong>Mana Point Enhancements</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><span><strong>Damage: (1 MP)</strong> Increase the damage dealt by 2.</span></p></li><li><span><strong>Duration: (1 MP) </strong>Change the duration to 1 minute.</span></li></ul>",
